Package: episodes
Title: Build and format drug episodes for health-state transition modelling 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nirupama", "Tamvada", , "ntamvada@bccrc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build and format drug episodes with health transition states from drug prescription data. Outputs can be fed into a health economic model for cost-effectiveness calculations.
